1DD7F3D1.Line13.137EC4: The Triune has tried to take it before. Cubs looking to prove their worth. They learned their place, but remain persistent.

67708DA0.Line3.137EC4: It is an heirloom of Raekor, Warmaster of change. Its edge claimed countless demons upon Arreat, yet showed no wear.

8EECE3DE.Line1.137EC4: The great axe of the Oxen Tribe has gone missing from the forge. Stolen by swift hands.

F65B9D93.Line15.137EC4: We’ve seen them hiding around the ruins on the southern coast. If they have the axe, it's sure to be there.
